*Teško* se moglo videti šta se dešava u mraku. (It was hard to see what was happening in the dark.)

Njegovo oboljenje je *teško*. (His illness is severe.)

*Teško* je bilo odrediti ko je kriv. (It was hard to determine who is guilty.)

Mislim da će se ovo *teško* zaboraviti. (I think this will be hard to forget.)

U poslednje vreme je *teško* živeti. (It has been hard to live lately.)

Nešto se čudno dešava, ali *teško* je reći šta je to. (Something strange is happening, but it is hard to say what it is.)